channel.title: MoparScape 3.1 help
channel.description:
Ok, I was starting up MS 3.1 (no web) and I got this: [04:11:41] Starting MoparScape 3.1 [04:11:41] Playing 0-hangar.mid [04:11:41] [04:11:41] [04:11:41] Loaded 0 random handlers [04:11:41] # Loading controllers [04:11:42] Loading config from ./Aryan/Configs/defaults.txt [04:11:42] [04:11:42] News: MoparScape 3.2 is now released, download it from [04:11:42] News: http://www.moparisthebest.com/moparscape.html [04:11:42] News: Or use the webclient at moparisthebest.com [04:11:42] News: I am now shutting down your moparscape 3.1 [04:11:42] News: [04:11:42] News: -moparisthebest Press any key to continue . . .
And it wont open up the client...[br][size=1]Posted at: November 09, 2006, 05:01:50 PM[/size][hr]Nevermind...Figured it out!
